  <h1>8 AI Automations Swiss SMEs Can Use Right Now</h1>

  <p class="intro">Not every automation is worth it – but these 8 are. They're based on real projects with Swiss companies, agencies and freelancers. Each use case includes concrete time savings and guidance on who it fits best.</p>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">01</div>
    <h2>Email Triage &amp; Draft Replies</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ ~1 hr / day saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Executives, Sales, Customer Service</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>50–100 emails daily. Much of it irrelevant or routine. Urgent items get buried. Replies cost focus and time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>AI automatically classifies by priority, filters out noise and suggests appropriate reply drafts – directly in your inbox.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Supported tools: <strong>Outlook, Gmail, Apple Mail</strong>. No switching required.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">02</div>
    <h2>Automated Proposals &amp; Quotes</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 3–5 hrs / week saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Agencies, Consultants, Freelancers</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Every proposal has the same basic structure – yet takes 1–2 hours each time. Texts are rewritten over and over.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Short briefing input → complete, brand-compliant proposal with pricing, scope description and deliverables. Minutes instead of hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Output: <strong>PDF, Word or sent directly by email</strong>. Your own corporate design.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">03</div>
    <h2>Automated Weekly Reporting</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 2–4 hrs / week saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Project managers, teams with reporting obligations</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Data has to be manually gathered from JIRA, Toggl, Google Sheets or other tools and copy-pasted into a report.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Automatic data pull from all relevant sources → finished report as PDF or Google Slides – every Monday at 8am in your inbox.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Sources: <strong>JIRA, Toggl, Harvest, Asana, Google Sheets, Excel</strong> – all combinable.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">04</div>
    <h2>Invoicing &amp; Bookkeeping Preparation</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 2–3 hrs / month saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Freelancers, agencies, service providers</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Export hours from Toggl or Harvest, create invoice in Word/Excel, save as PDF, send by email – all done manually.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Toggl tracking → invoice PDF with your logo → automatically sent to the client. Month-end without manual work.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Compatible with: <strong>Toggl, Harvest, VAT-compliant PDF templates</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">05</div>
    <h2>Client Correspondence &amp; Follow-ups</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 1–2 hrs / week saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Sales, consultants, account management</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Follow-up emails after meetings get forgotten. Proposals go without follow-through. Leads go cold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Automatic reminders + ready-made email drafts based on the last contact. No lead gets lost again.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Integration with: <strong>CRM, Outlook, Gmail, Calendar</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">06</div>
    <h2>Document Research &amp; Summaries</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 3–6 hrs / week saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Lawyers, consultants, management</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Reading long PDFs, contracts and reports takes hours. Relevant information is hard to find.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>AI summarises documents, answers questions about them and extracts relevant clauses or figures – in seconds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Supports: <strong>PDF, Word, Excel, email attachments</strong>. Fully local possible (no cloud upload).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">07</div>
    <h2>Social Media Content at the Push of a Button</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 2–4 hrs / week saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 Marketing, freelancers with an online presence</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>Regular posts on LinkedIn or Instagram take time. Coming up with new texts in the right tone over and over is exhausting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Enter a topic → finished posts in your tone of voice for LinkedIn, Instagram or newsletters. Ready to publish or for review.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Channels: <strong>LinkedIn, Instagram, Newsletter (Mailchimp, Brevo)</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="uc-card">
    <div class="uc-num">08</div>
    <h2>Internal Processes &amp; Onboarding</h2>
    <div class="uc-meta">
      <span class="tag tag-save">⏱ 5–10 hrs / new team member saved</span>
      <span class="tag tag-fit">👤 HR, team leads, ops</span>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Problem</div>
        <p>A new team member costs 1–2 weeks of manual onboarding. Checklists, accesses, documents – everything gets organised from scratch each time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-box">
        <div class="uc-box-label">Solution</div>
        <p>Automated onboarding sequence: set up accesses, send checklists, assign documents – all without manual effort.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">Compatible with: <strong>Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, Notion, Confluence</strong>.</p>
  </div>

